          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Eden’s river has a purpose,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bringing life where’er it goes;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s salvation, like a river,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Goes through stages as it flows."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "First we’re saved from Satan’s tyranny,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And later, we will see, from Christianity."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God is flowing in recovery,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just open up to Him and see."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not just individual Christians,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Isolated, wand’ring free,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But as stones built up together,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ expressing corporately."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We were saved just Jesus to contain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But there’s a reason too,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That Christ came into you;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He came in, His purpose to secure,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To gain for Him a bride so pure."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not the stones, though very precious,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Elevated “spiritually,”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But the stones built up together"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the Spirit, practically."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You will ne’er be fully satisfied,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Or be content inside,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Till Jesus has His Bride."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Did you know the Lord is seeking you"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To build into His building true?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    }
